tle> ToT Strats?</span><hr size=1> We're practicing a lot and I seem to draw quite a bit of attention right off the bat.  Basically, the other team's tanks are grouped with a bard for running speed and their main goal seems to be to shred me quickly.  Any suggestions to combat this?  Also, what other tactics can we wizzies use to perform well in this type combat?<br>
